data.description: BACK UP Offers Accepted ......The one you've been waiting for!!! One Owner, END UNIT on rear corner,  2 Full & 2 half baths 3/2 bedrooms -- LOTS OF WINDOWS/Great Light! - Custom Hunter Douglas Sun Shades on main & CUSTOM Plantation Shutters on upper level - Nice double pane Windows, Brand New Front Door & Sidelight, NEW Sliding Door to Deck, hose bib on deck for watering flowers,  NEW Deck w/ TREX & NEW Railing, UPDATED KITCHEN, NEW GRANITE, NEW APPLIANCES, NEW LED RECESSED LIGHTS, Freshly painted Cabinets, NEW 1/2 Bath in LL,  Enter either thru driveway/1 car garage or Side entrance, Main Level has Foyer, Living Room, Dining Room, Pass through Kitchen, Laundry Room, 1/2 bath - Head upstairs to 2 Large Bedrooms with Vaulted Ceilings, Updated  Owner's Bath w/ Jacuzzi Jet Soaking Tub, Stall Shower, double Vanity in Owners En-suite, Head downstairs to 3rd bedroom/Rec Room/Home Office & see NEW 1/2 bathroom, Extra storage closet &  a walk out Patio with country swing. Low condo fee.  Close to 270, Shopping & Clarksburg Outlets.
